["Kohala is a small village near Mysore in Karnataka province of India.","Kohala is located on the Mananthavady road at a distance of 197\u00a0km from the provincial capital of Bangalore. The Postal code of Kohala is 571125-Hampapura.[1]  The nearby villages are Nanjangud and Krishnarajasagara.","The government Lower Primary school is the only educational organization of Kohala.[2]"]